Detects periodic outbound traffic patterns that may indicate malware beaconing to a command-and-control server.

index=network OR index=proxy
| bin _time span=5m
| stats count by src_ip _time
| eventstats avg(count) as avg stdev(count) as stdev by src_ip
| eval is_beaconing=if(count > (avg + (stdev*3)), "YES", "NO")
| search is_beaconing="YES"
